</m:msup>
<m:mo> ) </m:mo>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> ab </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 6 </m:mn>
<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mo> x </m:mo>
<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mo> ( </m:mo>
<m:mn> 12 </m:mn>
<m:mo> ) </m:mo>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 3 </m:mn>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-212">
Putting in the expression of cosine, we have :
</para>
<para id="element-214">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> cos </m:mi>
<m:mi> θ </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mfrac>
<m:mrow>
<m:mi mathvariant="bold"> a </m:mi>
<m:mo mathvariant="bold"> . </m:mo>
<m:mi mathvariant="bold"> b </m:mi>
</m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mi> ab </m:mi>
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mfrac>
<m:mrow>
<m:mn> 3 </m:mn>
</m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 3 </m:mn>
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mfrac>
<m:mrow>
<m:mo> √ </m:mo>
<m:mn> 3 </m:mn>
</m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
